        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事庫克警示私募信貸風險 稱或給金融體系帶來壓力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克表示，鑒於槓桿化企業的「複雜性和相互關聯性增加」，官員們應監測私募信貸中意外損失可能如何蔓延至更廣泛的美國金融體系。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">庫克周四表示，她關注從近期破產案例中可見的實物支付安排使用增加中可以學到什麼。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「當這些安排的敞口規模和複雜程度缺乏透明度、當一個行業經歷快速成長期、以及當這些安排尚未經歷完整的信貸周期時，我們更有可能看到類似近期新聞報導的案例再次出現，」她在為喬治城大學活動中準備的發言稿中表示。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-993e8bc4-2d48-3d27-89b0-345b520f7c28-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她還表示，最近汽車行業的私營企業破產也暴露出銀行、對沖基金和專業金融公司在內的廣泛金融實體的意外損失和風險敞口。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">庫克的表態與聯儲會理事Michael Barr本周早些時候的言論相呼應。Barr當時指出，私募信貸是潛在風險領域之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Cook Keeping Close Eye on Private Credit, Asset Valuations</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Amara Omeokwe.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%A8%B1%E6%88%96%E7%B5%A6%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-171157782.html",
